data.description: Charming 4 bedroom, 4 BATHROOM Townhome in the Heart of Henderson. Conveniently located near shopping plazas, schools, and easy access to the 95 freeway. This home features a downstairs Primary Bedroom adjacent to the Primary Full bathroom with dual sinks, and an additional 1/2 bathroom on the first floor, granite countertops, and recessed lighting. This home is minutes away from the Lake Mead National Recreation Area and easy access to the 215 and 95 Freeways. MUST SEE!
